OL,7,FA Jersey charity that provides
OL,8,Ftraining, education and jobs for
OL,9,Fpeople with learning disabilities and
OL,10,Fautism has announced that it will be
OL,11,Fclosing one of its two cafes.
OL,13,FBeresford Street Kitchen will shut the
OL,14,FLa Hougue Bie Tea Rooms in November,
OL,15,Fblaming financial challenges.
OL,17,FChief Executive Officer Gabby Ellmers
OL,18,Fsays: "Like many charities, Beresford
OL,19,FStreet Kitchen has been significantly
OL,20,Fimpacted by increased costs and
OL,21,Freduced funding.
