OL,7,F"We are also struggling with the
OL,8,Frising cost of sales and reducing
OL,9,Fprofits in our social enterprise areas
OL,10,Fand have decided to close La Hougue
OL,11,FBie Tea Rooms ahead of the winter low
OL,12,Fseason."
OL,14,FHowever, she reassures islanders that
OL,15,Fthe rest of its operations, including
OL,16,Fthe other cafe in St Helier, will not
OL,17,Fbe affected and there are no job
OL,18,Flosses as staff will be reassigned.
