OL,8,Ffirst customers in 2020, opening at
OL,9,Fthe historic site in partnership with
OL,10,FJersey Heritage.
OL,12,FMs Ellmers adds: "It has been a great
OL,13,Ffour-year partnership ... We remain
OL,14,Fcommitted to our mission and will
OL,15,Fcontinue to provide over 40,000 hours
OL,16,Fa year of education, training and
OL,17,Femployment for the 63 crew on our
OL,18,Fprogrammes.
