OL,7,F"We are optimistic that once we
OL,8,Fnavigate through these challenging
OL,9,Ftimes, we can continue to develop our
OL,10,Fvaluable programmes to support people
OL,11,Fwith learning disabilities and
OL,12,Fautistic people to reach their
OL,13,Findependence and employability goals.
OL,15,F"We will be focusing on our core
OL,16,Fobjectives and on reinvigorating the
OL,17,Ftown cafe. The decision to close La
OL,18,FHougue Bie Tea Rooms aims to
OL,19,Fcontribute to the sustainability of
OL,20,Fthe charity."
